https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p2qXlKkmRIeQP6GgHTpilAdLdaZ.jpg Alton & Kenya's OUTRAGEOUS WEDDING is a romantic comedy about a wedding. The bride and groom, Alton Sheffield and Kenya Jackson, grew up on different sides of the track. Alton grew up in an upper class household in Baldwin Hills. His wife to be, Kenya, grew up in the "Jungle" (South Central LA). Comedy ensues as the two families come together for a day of holy matrimony. Alton & Kenya's Outrageous Wedding
